      <p style="text-align: center;font-size: large;margin-bottom: 30px;">
      What if there was one place where people looking for a property could do all their research?  One place to collect all the information about properties they are interested in - schools nearby, parking, crime-rates etc.  And what if with a click they could share this information with their friends to get feedback and advice? Well, that is exactly what PickingPlaces provides.
